data.description: Introducing this stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom house in Kingston, TN! This property is the perfect epitome of comfortable and stylish living. Nestled on Fox Fire Ln, this charming abode is now available for sale. With a total livable area of 3024 sqft, there is plenty of space for you and your loved ones to enjoy.Step inside this exquisite home and be greeted by a spacious living area, perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with your family. The large windows allow natural light to flood the space, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The new sleek LVP floors throughout the main level add a touch of elegance to the overall interior.The new remodeled kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or whipping up a quick meal, this kitchen will surely be your favorite space in the house. The adjacent dining area provides a cozy spot for enjoying meals together.On the main  floor, you'll find the four comfortable and well-appointed bedrooms. Each bedroom offers a peaceful retreat, perfect for unwinding after a long day. The master bedroom and bathroom are very spacious, with a walk-in tile shower and jetted tub ready for you to relax in, the three bathrooms are tastefully designed and provide convenience and privacy for all occupants. The basement has a rec.room and a home theater with kitchenette and seating, ready to watch a family movie.In addition to its impressive interior, this property boasts a fantastic location. Situated in one of Kingston's sought-after neighborhoods, you'll have easy access to amenities such as schools, shopping centers, and recreational facilities. The peaceful and friendly community make this house desirable for families and individuals alike.The property was built in 1979, showcasing its timeless architecture and durability. The energy class of this house is A+, making it efficient and eco-friendly. The property will be available for you to move in at closing.Priced at $525,000, this house is a fantastic investment opportunity. Don't miss out on the chance to own this remarkable property. Experience the easy and comfortable lifestyle that awaits you at 228 Fox Fire Ln. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this dream house your forever home!
